    All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MapDigesterLocatorForFiles, MapDigesterLocatorForGMaps

    public abstract class MapDigesterLocator<CircleFindingsPairType extends craj.mapDigesterLocator.CircleFindingsPair>
extends GenericObservable<CircleFindingsPairType>
implements GenericObserver<java.util.List<CircleFinding>>
    This abstract class implements the functionality of creating as much as CircleFinderThread objects as processor cores are available. It is possible to wait for the completion of the calculation of all files with the wait-method. If the calculation of an image completes, the observing objects are notified with the circle findings.
